import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'; import Accordion from 'react-bootstrap/Accordion'; import { useState, useEffect } from 'react'; import { useParams } from 'react-router-dom'; const ProductNavbar = ({activeTab}) => { const params = useParams(); const productid = params.productid; /*To open accordion based on category of item 0 is Supplements, 1 is Injury, 2 is Illness, the rest is others*/ const [category, setCategory] = useState(""); console.log("proeuct category:" + category); useEffect(()=>{ if( (productid === "brain-boosters-memory-enhancers") || (productid === "heart-health") || (productid === "joint-health") || (productid === "liver-tonic") || (productid === "natural-antioxidants") || (productid === "hormones-oral-contraceptives") || (productid === "slimming-weight-management") ) { setCategory("0"); } else if( (productid === "blunt-trauma") || (productid === "muscle-relaxants") || (productid === "wound-healing") ) { setCategory("1"); } else if ( (productid === "cough-cold") || (productid === "ear-nose-throat") || (productid === "urinary-incontinence") ) { setCategory("2"); } else if (productid === "dermatological") { setCategory("3"); } else if (productid === "disinfectants") { setCategory("4"); } else if (productid === "medical-tools") { setCategory("5"); } else { setCategory("0"); } }, [productid, category]) return ( <> Supplements
  • Brain boosters / Memory enhancers
  • Heart health
  • Joint health
  • Liver tonic
  • Natural anti-oxidants
  • Hormones / Oral contraceptives
  • Slimming / Weight management
Injury
  • Blunt trauma
  • Muscle relaxants
  • Wound healing
 Illness
  • Cough & cold preparations
  • Ear, nose & throat preparations
  • Urinary incontinence
 Dermatological Disinfectants Medical Tools ); } export default ProductNavbar;
